
TEST CASES FOR raeselect

Search Buttons
1. Enter (broad) search parameters, press search
2. Verify Next/Prev buttons move through results as expected

Refine Search
1. Enter search parameters, press search
2. Press refine button
3. Verify search form values still intact

Invalid Search
1. Enter invalid search parameters (e.g. letters in date field), press search
2. Verify problems are detected and displayed

New Search
1. Enter search parameters, press search
2. Press new button
3. Verify search form values cleared

Add RAE Item(s)
1. Enter search parameters, press search
2. Click add button next to an item in results list
3. Check DB - item added to rae_selected table
4. Verify item is now listed as 'already selected' in results list
5. Reload page, verify item is still listed as selected
6. Repeat 1-5 for other items

Remove RAE Item(s)
1. Enter search parameters (same as previous test), press search
2. Click remove button next to an item in selected list
3. Check DB - item removed from rae_selected table
4. Verify item is no longer listed as 'already selected' in results list
5. Reload page, verify item is no longer listed as selected
6. Repeat 2-5 for other selected items

Multi-user Item
1. Carry out steps 1-5 from "Add RAE Item(s)"
2. Log in as different user
3. Locate item via search (use search search parameters)
4. Verify item is 'selected by..' in results list
5. Click add button next to item in results list
6. Verify item is 'also selected by..' in results list



